{"tid":220784,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"6個月大的狗隻點食杜蟲藥","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T11:05:46.000Z","uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e25e0a98eb130e78cb4fa8a9afd4e282ed2cf04","tid":220784,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"我隻狗食緊x圖<br />\n買藥個陣，個老闆叫我每個月比狗食一次半粒<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/28/161241_e010171b7968a86194ec1469fbbc3383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F161241_e010171b7968a86194ec1469fbbc3383.jpg&h=61caba6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我隻狗宜家8.5kg，6個月多d了。<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪應該每3個月食一粒？"},{"pid":"88ef4ac1bae97b5f8602281c893db551b26f40b9","tid":220784,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"我都係食呢隻 咁你咪畀一粒佢"},{"pid":"2af9e77889b07a09d5e2e47b8133647bbaf4fd65","tid":220784,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"如果之前未杜過蟲 就要跟份量連杜三日 第一次和第三次最好相隔48-49小時<br />\n<br />\n杜過就跟説明書方法杜<br />\n<br />\n如果狗狗是剛回家  就要連杜三日"}]}